OL,3,CBaby suffered head injury when pram
OL,4,Crolled into 35mph train, report
OL,6,FA two-month-old baby suffered a head
OL,7,Finjury when their pram rolled into the
OL,8,Fside of a train travelling at 35mph, a
OL,9,Freport has revealed.
OL,11,FThe collision caused the pram to tip
OL,12,Fover, resulting in the infant falling
OL,13,Fonto the platform at Banbury station,
OL,14,FOxfordshire, the Rail Accident
OL,15,FInvestigation Branch (RAIB) said.
OL,17,FThe incident at 12.26pm on June 8
OL,18,Fhappened because the baby's parent
OL,19,F"momentarily released" the pram,
OL,20,Faccording to the report.
