OL,3,CBaby suffered head injury when pram
OL,4,Crolled into 35mph train, report
OL,6,FCCTV footage shows that in the
OL,7,Fprevious 10 minutes, the parent was
OL,8,F"either very close or in direct
OL,9,Fcontact" with the pram.
OL,11,FAround 15 seconds before the accident,
OL,12,Fthey moved the pram closer to the
OL,13,Farriving train to prepare to board it.
OL,15,FWith the pram's front wheels touching
OL,16,Fthe yellow safety line, the parent put
OL,17,Fone hand on a piece of luggage and
OL,18,Fturned to face a relative,
OL,19,F"momentarily letting go of the pram",
OL,20,Fthe report said.
