OL,3,CBaby suffered head injury when pram
OL,4,Crolled into 35mph train, report
OL,6,FFollowing the accident, Chiltern
OL,7,FRailways, which operates the station,
OL,8,Finstalled additional signage which
OL,9,Fincludes instructions to help prevent
OL,10,Fsimilar incidents from occurring, the
OL,11,FRAIB said.
OL,13,FChiltern Railways and station owner
OL,14,FNetwork Rail both have
OL,15,Fresponsibilities for its safety and
OL,16,Fmaintenance.
OL,18,FA Chiltern Railways spokesperson said:
OL,19,F"The safety of our customers when at
OL,20,Four stations or on board our services
OL,21,Fis our top priority.
