OL,3,CBaby suffered head injury when pram
OL,4,Crolled into 35mph train, report
OL,6,F"Our station staff looked after the
OL,7,Ffamily involved in this incident,
OL,8,Fcalled an ambulance and supported the
OL,9,Ffamily whilst the paramedics arrived.
OL,11,F"We have since installed additional
OL,12,Fsignage at Banbury Station which
OL,13,Freminds customers to remain vigilant
OL,14,Fand safe on the platforms."
OL,16,FNetwork Rail has been approached for a
OL,17,Fcomment.
